public final class Jsonschema
extends com.google.api.client.json.GenericJson

Model definition for Discovery.Jsonschema. This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Discovery service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need. For a detailed explanation, see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json
